#-------Run pytest-------------
From IDE
OR
From Terminal:
--- To Run all tests inside the package
-v = verbose(verbose is an argument which is used to report more information about an opertaion)
–s = to see the console log
py.test -v -s 'filepath'
py.test -v -s C:\Users\lm\PycharmProjects\Pytest\TestData


-----Run using the file name
py.test -v -s filename
py.test -v -s demo_test1.py


-----Run using the method name
py.test -v -s filename::methodname
py.test -v -s demo_test1.py::test_one

py.test  syntax.py –v –s ----to run specific file
py.test -k CreditCard -v –s --- regular expression
py.test -m smoke -v –s ---- tag


#----------rerun failed tests
py.test --reruns 4 test_demo.py
